author: Jessica Barnes (Mrs. HipsnHustle)
title: Jessica Barnes (Mrs. HipsnHustle)
text: I couldn't have been more happy with the service and patience they took to get my order right. After emailing back and forth I finalized my order and the 2 inch , 85 lbs marker was shipped to my home in a week. It was beautiful. I shopped several places but I am so glad I went here.
